Package fakestore.view

package fakestore.view
This package contains the view classes of the FakeStore. The view is responsible for displaying the current state of the application.

This package contains IView which is the interface the controller can use to communicate. The implementation View does use the interfaces IRoute, IClickable and ITypeControl so that the controller can properly utilize the view.
